EXPECT_CONTAINS alveg
EXPECT_NO_AUTOCORRECT

SCENARIO nogg offers nóg via the gemination-accent composition
T "ekki nogg"
EXPECT_CONTAINS nóg
EXPECT_NO_AUTOCORRECT

SCENARIO awgke mash stays uncorrected and verbatim-led
T "sem awgke"
EXPECT_VERBATIM awgke
EXPECT_NO_AUTOCORRECT
